snippet.title: Moo Lander Multiplayer Tournament - PAX/EGX 2020
snippet.description:
Do you want a chance to win $50? 💲
Do you want to have YOUR OWN branded multiplayer Cow map in Moo Lander? 🎮

For this year’s PAX & EGX we've prepared something special – a ⚔️FIERCE MULTIPLAYER CONTEST ⚔️ with awesome rewards!

🕑 It is starting today. Join us - the clock is ticking! 🕑
🐮 We will meet you on the battlefields of Moo Lander! 🐮

How to participate: http://moolander.com/contest
Download Moo Lander Demo: http://moolander.com/steam
